parameter.val: "Kittens sometimes go through a phase in which they believe dogs (or even rabbits) are sentient, not that different from cats. This illusion fades quickly upon first talking to those animals, as their vastly inferior intellect is undeniable. Ruling them is not a privilege we steal, but a burden we must bear." -Violet, grandmother of Amethyst
